{
  "id": "RAW_b8ae49e4",
  "title": "KDD 2026｜小红书搜索：生成式相关性让搜索“会思考”",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4OTc2MzczNg==&mid=2247494127&idx=1&sn=d1092d3c09f5cf253f73f1b750107b7e",
  "date": "2025-12-09 07:03:00",
  "author": "小红书技术REDtech",
  "siteName": "小红书技术REDtech",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 10px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin: 10px 0% 8px;text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;width: 100%;border-left: 3px solid rgb(219, 219, 219);border-bottom-left-radius: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 8px;align-self: flex-start;background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);text-align: justify;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p data-slate-node=\"element\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\">相关性是搜索最基础最重要的信号，旨在衡量搜索结果与用户查询的匹配程度。传统判别式模型直接输出标签或分数，在复杂语义建模方面能力有限。推动相关性建模从判别式向生成式演进，并融入思维链（Chain-of-Thought）推理能力，已成为重要研究方向。然而，现有方法大多依赖大量人工标注或合成的思维链数据进行监督微调，导致模型泛化能力不足，同时领域无关、自由形式的推理往往过于笼统，难以满足工业场景中复杂的业务标准。为解决上述问题，小红书搜索团队提出分段优势掩码策略（Stepwise Advantage Masking, SAM），在多步骤推理中引入轻量级过程监督，改进强化学习中的信用分配机制，从而提升模型对复杂业务相关性标准的理解与内化能力。该方法在业务实践中取得显著效果，相关研究成果已被 KDD 2026 录用。</span></span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文标题：</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Optimizing Generative Ranking Relevance via Reinforcement Learning in Xiaohongshu Search</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文地址：</span><span style=\"background-color: rgba(1, 0, 0, 0);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.00968\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.00968</a></span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010459\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b7cf9769&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJGSf2HoTNE01uunVibFf7Rtv7dXVG0Y6bibwlCQhB1MqBqbmicDYJflVlw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在当今互联网时代，搜索引擎已经成为人们获取信息的第一入口。无论是谷歌还是小红书，每天都有海量用户在搜索框中输入问题，希望得到最合适、最有价值的内容列表。然而，想要真正让用户满意，并不是把“最热门”的结果排在前面那么简单——核心挑战在于：什么才是“相关”的？系统怎样判断一条内容和用户的搜索意图是否真的匹配？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统的搜索相关性模型大多是判别式模型，它们接收一个“查询 + 内容”的组合，然后输出一个分数或概率，表示两者是否相关。这类模型虽然运行稳定，但有两个长期痛点：（1）像黑盒一样，不解释理由：模型给出“相关/不相关”，却无法说明为什么，导致搜索业务同学也难以判断模型犯错的原因；（2）理解能力有限：用户搜索意图越来越复杂，仅靠单一分值，很难捕捉语义细节，比如隐含需求、场景差异、跨概念关联等。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着大语言模型（Large Language Models，LLMs）的快速发展，搜索行业开始尝试一种全新的相关性建模方式 —— 生成式相关性模型（Generative Relevance Models, GRMs）。与传统只输出一个数字的模型不同，GRMs 会像人一样“解释过程”：先分析，再推理，然后再给结论，使搜索排序不仅更准确，也更可解释。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010462\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7017543859649122\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"912\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83b8b1a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJdLGLJR442K6oVgXh4T3x4TGKEBNfuzpcn8icE4yFrnRw2JeYD6iba2kg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);font-size: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个实例说明了显式推理增强了相关性评估的可解释性和有效性。对于查询“为什么植物需要光来生长？”，基于推理的模型利用与光合作用相关内容识别出部分相关性，而没有推理的模型则无法识别这种联系。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">但目前行业方案仍面临两大瓶颈：（1）大多数方法依赖人工或其他模型合成的推理数据，成本极高且最终模型泛化性不足；（2）开域搜索语义复杂、意图多变，仅靠通用推理很难稳定泛化，尤其是小红书这种开放内容生态中，用户搜索话题覆盖生活、商品、问答、知识等多维场景，推理逻辑如果没有领域规则指引，往往会“想太多或者想错方向”，和业务团队的预期相差较远。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010460\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b23cc3b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJO2dW131qwFsjiaofE4hM95MMwRTMllGyMgmNicCksQaCOYbsFrmXdYUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对以上挑战，我们提出了一种在小红书搜索中生成式相关性建模新范式：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于强化学习的生成式推理相关性建模框架。&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心思想是 ——&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">让模型像人类评审员一样遵循规则、循序推理，而不是一上来拍脑袋给答案。</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">整个方案有两个关键设计：</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.1&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">将相关性建模转化为基于相关性标准的分步推理任务</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">模型不再直接输出标签，而是通过类似 Chain-of-Thought 的方式进行多步推理。我们直接接入：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小红书内部专家制定通用的相关性标准</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对模糊场景的细则</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些规则就像“行业版数学公理”，让模型不再盲猜，而是</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">带着业务知识思考。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">这也是我们能在开放领域搜索中取得显著提升的关键原因。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010463\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9401709401709402\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"936\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4ed49107&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJx1znvOglhTWooLtj9xkp3hSpLmrWhuiaPxJGicPkcUaaBVPbBVEewGfQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">总的来说共分为三大步：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">通用语义理解：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">查询与内容是否同类目、同主题、关键词是否有命中、核心内容占比是否足够多、通用的相关性打分是多少</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">规则约束：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">是否触发业务发展所积累的特殊case（如多实体对比、问答等特殊场景）</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果反思：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">依据前两步综合得出最终等级（共 5 档分级）</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样，模型输出的不仅是一个无法解释的相关性档位，而是一条</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">有解释、有逻辑、有依据的推理链。</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.2 Stepwise Advantage Masking（SAM）：让 RL 真正学会“思考相关性”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010468\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0e191590&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJ2rqjA6LTgGPu6Xlxic8kSNxqSY2tvLKd7iahfpz4blXLlicglNb6lQuuA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统强化学习做相关性任务只看最终结果对不对，但在推理任务中：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">最终答案错，不代表前面每步都错；</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">最终答案对，也可能是瞎蒙的。</span></span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">SAM 的贡献就在于解决这一痛点：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在推理链每一步让模型给出中间分数；</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">自动比对每一步是否正确；</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">只奖励正确的推理步骤，只惩罚真正有问题的步骤。</span></strong></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这让模型能够：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">学到可复用的推理逻辑；</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">避免错误逻辑被强化；&nbsp;</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">过程监督的训练效率远高于人工训练过程监督模型或在线价值估计；</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">一句话总结：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">SAM 让强化学习从“只看结果”变为“理解过程”</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010467\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1877637130801688\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"948\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2741100f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJnQwYVWlc7oC7x7OM5uBtm6T82xXDCQMyymiaDicz3ciavP21UBbfkHM3A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">总的来说，我们的工作首次在小红书搜索中验证了一条可规模化落地的新路径：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">用 RL 驱动生成式相关性判断，通过规则引导推理链，并利用 SAM 精准分配奖励信号。</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010474\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJFJSIprxmg6c21F7gjf8o4LuVibpG7nOn1RGZYWW9fuKuaRQJbM9icEAg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"558\" data-cropsely2=\"155\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b7e368a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJFJSIprxmg6c21F7gjf8o4LuVibpG7nOn1RGZYWW9fuKuaRQJbM9icEAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.1 离线指标</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">为了全面地衡量线上分布，我们使用了两个基准数据集：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">RANDOM</span>&nbsp;（随机分布）和&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">LONGTAIL</span>（长尾分布），每个数据集包含&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">15000 个&nbsp;</span>人工标注的&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">查询-笔记对</span>。</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010465\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.25925925925925924\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=197da99c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJvJUt3w6e6zSD5XPmzAsibr6oJ8WlVuTSCqbSeFZrEdtoydsP1kLaNjw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.1.1 推理机制对监督微调（SFT）有益还是有害？</span></strong></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验设置：</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于相同SFT初始化模型，在固定数据、提示和奖励定义下，在SFT范式下，对比不同数据类型（w/wo reasoning）差异。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">监督基线模型对比：</span></strong></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">SFT-Label（标签监督模型）</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n         <br> \n        </span></strong><span leaf=\"\">使用20万条纯标签数据训练，在RANDOM数据集上的2-ACC/5-ACC达90.26/78.64，在LONGTAIL数据集上达89.11/77.66，确立强基准性能。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">监督推理模型</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n         <br> \n        </span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">SFT-Reasoning v1：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">15万条思维链（CoT）数据训练</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span><span leaf=\"\">RANDOM：80.10/59.44</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span><span leaf=\"\">LONGTAIL：77.50/59.22</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">SFT-Reasoning v2：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">50万条CoT数据训练（数据量提升3.3倍）</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span><span leaf=\"\">RANDOM：83.04/63.06</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n        <br> \n       </span><span leaf=\"\">LONGTAIL：81.15/63.55</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"> \n         <br> \n        </span><span leaf=\"\">关键发现：</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">即使增加3.3倍训练数据，推理模型性能仍显著落后于纯标签模型（RANDOM数据集差距&gt;7%）</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">结论：</span></b><span leaf=\"\">直接引入多步推理链进行监督训练非但未提升效果，反而导致性能下降，这说明\"多步推理并不能天然提升排序质量\"。我们考虑，相较于纯优化 label 的 sft 方式，没有额外优化的带思维链的建模方式，由于其优化目标的增多，故而会导致指标天然不如前者。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">3.1.2 过程监督强化学习能否真正增强相关性推理？</span></span></p>\n    <blockquote>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">基于上述发现，我们认为引入强化学习（RL）对思维轨迹进行额外的筛选优化是十分必要的</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">实验设置：</span></span></p>\n    <p data-slate-node=\"element\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">基于相同SFT初始化模型，在固定数据、提示和奖励定义下，对比三种RL变体（PPO、OutcomeRL、ProcessRL），聚焦信用分配机制差异。</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">核心发现：</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv5vll1y5e\">\n     <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\" style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\">PPO-Reasoning</span></span></span></strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">：</span></span></span></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li>\n       <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwvcc1i9nj\">\n        <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在SFT基础上采用PPO进行训练，依赖价值函数估计进行信用分配。优点是相对SFT有提升；缺点是价值估计偏差与不稳定的信用分配，难以充分利用推理结构，性能仅在random测试集上优于基线。</span></span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv5vll1y5e\">\n     <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">2.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">OutcomeRL-Reasoning：</span></span></span></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li>\n       <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwvbkt817jw\">\n        <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">采用组级奖励归一化（归因到整条轨迹），避免价值估计误差并稳定策略优化。优点是整体性能优于PPO；局限是对轨迹中所有token均匀分配优势，无法区分各步对最终决策的真实贡献。</span></span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv5vll1y5e\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwvbmyr1pze\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">性能：RANDOM（80.90 5-ACC）、LONGTAIL（77.03 5-ACC），多数指标超越PPO</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwvbmyr1pze\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">局限</span><span textstyle=\"\">：轨迹内均匀分配奖励，忽略步骤贡献。</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n    <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv5vll1y5e\">\n     <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">ProcessRL-Reasoning（SAM机制）：</span></span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv90wr1tfx\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">该机制进行分步信用分配，将奖励更精确地归因到关键推理步骤，缓解虚假奖励传播，改善过程层面的学习信号质量。</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv93x97sc\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">综合性能最优：&nbsp;</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv93x97sc\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">RANDOM：81.23 5-ACC / 73.55 Macro F1</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv93x97sc\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">LONGTAIL：77.72 5-ACC / 66.39 Macro F1</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv9qgl1t7i\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">显著提升稳健性与泛化能力（Macro F1指标）</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p data-slate-node=\"element\" data-xhs-node-propsblock-id=\"&quot;3755d67f3effc7cd306aef1bffa21ef7&quot;\" data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\" data-xhs-node-propsupdate=\"&quot;500027269_2025-12-04T11:14:04.453Z&quot;\"><strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\" style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">结论</span></span></span></strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">：</span></span></span></p>\n    <p data-mpa-md-root=\"t\" data-mpa-md-key=\"bullet-list\" data-mpa-action-id=\"miwv8rbhmb2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv8ra9t5w\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">分步信用分配（SAM）较均匀分配（OutcomeRL）带来持续增益，尤其在复杂场景（LONGTAIL）。</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <p></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type:disc;padding-left:1.2em;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\" data-mpa-md-content=\"t\" data-mpa-md-action-id=\"miwv8svwcpj\">\n       <p><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">信用分配机制是优化推理模型的关键因素，SAM机制实现最均衡的性能提升。</span></span></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 18px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 36, 66);\">3.2 在线指标</span></span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">teacher model 效果蒸馏到一个轻量级的 0.1B &nbsp;BERT 模型中进行在线实验</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010466\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4139344262295082\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"488\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8aff579&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJ3hUm58Wsw0ricSAA5ZgQAJD1XywbQQkIJZPkwpQQs7gDDQHpo4W55Gg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p data-slate-node=\"element\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500027269&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">我们做了为期7天的线上实验，</span></span></span><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">在</span></span></span><strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\" style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">用户互动</span></span></span></strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">与</span></span></span><strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\" style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">检索结果相关性</span></span></span></strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">两方面均取得了</span></span></span><strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\" style=\"color: var(--tw-prose-bold);font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">显著且可量化的双重提升</span></span></span></strong><span data-xhs-node-propsau=\"&quot;500025440&quot;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">。结果证明了方案的有效性。</span></span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010473\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/vxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJnejalfE2B6QU039undp2Y0SYicnOUiarbEw0nOd86icAz4y4fbofJ7pCA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"558\" data-cropsely2=\"155\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cd2dc4d9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJnejalfE2B6QU039undp2Y0SYicnOUiarbEw0nOd86icAz4y4fbofJ7pCA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"color: rgb(160, 160, 160);text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n    <blockquote>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">我们的长期目标是一次性训练模型，使业务团队能够在提示词中动态更新准则，从而让模型适应不断演变的业务逻辑。</span></p>\n    </blockquote>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">我们将这一概念称为“Instruction Relevance-LLM”。该模型能够通过利用一套持续更新的规则来适应变化的业务需求。然而，实验结果显示，当前经强化学习（RL）微调的模型对训练期间使用的固定规则集发生了过拟合。当在推理阶段修改规则时，模型仍倾向于基于训练中学到的原始逻辑进行推理。我们推测，这种现象的原因在于RL训练期间的准则体系是静态的，模型未曾接触到动态的规则变化。未来工作将重点在训练过程中引入动态准则的变化，以提升鲁棒性并降低过拟合，确保模型在推理阶段能更有效地处理准则修改。</span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010469\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2777777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a09d7545&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FvxnkL2N86ItR42MNvNBI7gkcl3USEaIJkeAABv9SOFv6ObAQ07hEyuJQic4icMLzzBpNKpZy1NFicic7yO3ZxvxCqg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">曾子洋</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">现硕士就读于北京邮电大学，小红书社区搜索算法实习生，主要研究方向：信息检索、大语言模型、强化学习。作为第一作者，已在CCF A/B类顶级国际会议（如 KDD、EMNLP）和计算机科学领域的 JCR Q1 期刊上发表论文 3 篇，常活跃于开源社区和知乎平台进行技术分享。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">华安</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小红书社区搜索高级算法工程师，主要方向搜索、自然语言处理、大语言模型、强化学习等。硕士毕业于复旦大学，在CCF A/B类国际会议（如 KDD、ICDE等）上发表多篇论文。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">星桓</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小红书社区搜索高级算法工程师，主要方向搜索、自然语言处理、大语言模型、知识图谱等。硕士毕业于复旦大学，在KDD、AAAI、ICDE等A类会议上发表多篇论文。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">深海</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">小红书搜索相关性负责人，推动小红书搜索向下一代搜索演进，硕士毕业于北京理工大学，在信息检索领域有丰富的落地实践经验，发表相关论文 10 余篇。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "小红书提出一种基于强化学习的生成式相关性建模框架，通过分段优势掩码策略（SAM）实现轻量级过程监督，提升大模型在搜索场景下的复杂语义理解和推理能力，并已被 KDD 2026 录用。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "小红书提出一种基于强化学习的生成式相关性建模框架，通过分段优势掩码策略（SAM）实现轻量级过程监督，提升大模型在搜索场景下的复杂语义理解和推理能力，并已被 KDD 2026 录用。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了小红书搜索团队如何将生成式相关性模型与强化学习结合，以应对传统判别式模型在复杂语义理解和可解释性方面的不足。核心方案是引入了“分段优势掩码策略”（SAM），通过在多步骤推理中引入轻量级过程监督，优化强化学习的信用分配机制。该方法将相关性评估转化为遵循小红书专家制定的相关性标准进行分步推理的任务，通过通用语义理解、规则约束和结果反思三步实现。SAM 策略的关键在于对强化学习过程进行精细化控制，仅奖励正确的推理步骤，从而有效避免错误逻辑被强化，显著提升了模型的学习效率和泛化能力。离线实验和 7 天线上 A/B 测试均验证了该方法的有效性，在用户互动和检索结果相关性方面取得了显著提升。文章最后展望了未来通过动态规则适应不断变化的业务逻辑的“Instruction Relevance-LLM”概念。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统搜索相关性模型面临语义理解受限和缺乏可解释性两大痛点。",
      "explanation": "判别式模型无法解释相关性判断的理由，且难以捕捉用户复杂的隐含需求和跨概念关联，导致黑盒问题和理解能力不足。"
    },
    {
      "point": "生成式相关性模型结合思维链（CoT）推理，可提供更准确、可解释的搜索结果。",
      "explanation": "模型通过分析、推理、给出结论的步骤，模拟人类思考过程，让搜索排序结果不仅更精准，也提供逻辑解释，增强了透明度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "小红书提出基于强化学习的生成式推理相关性建模框架，将相关性建模转化为多步骤推理任务。",
      "explanation": "模型不再直接输出标签，而是遵循小红书内部专家制定的相关性标准进行通用语义理解、规则约束和结果反思，实现有解释、有逻辑的推理链。"
    },
    {
      "point": "分段优势掩码策略（SAM）通过过程监督，解决了强化学习在推理任务中的信用分配问题。",
      "explanation": "SAM 在推理链每一步给出中间分数，并自动比对正确性，只奖励正确的推理步骤，避免错误逻辑被强化，促使模型真正理解推理过程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "线下实验和线上 A/B 测试均验证了 SAM 机制在提升搜索相关性和用户互动方面的显著效果。",
      "explanation": "与 SFT 基线模型和传统 RL 变体相比，SAM 在离线指标（如 Macro F1）和在线用户互动、检索结果相关性均有明显提升，证明了该方案的有效性。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "推动相关性建模从判别式向生成式演进，并融入思维链（Chain-of-Thought）推理能力，已成为重要研究方向。",
    "为解决上述问题，小红书搜索团队提出分段优势掩码策略（Stepwise Advantage Masking， SAM），在多步骤推理中引入轻量级过程监督，改进强化学习中的信用分配机制，从而提升模型对复杂业务相关性标准的理解与内化能力。",
    "生成式相关性模型（Generative Relevance Models， GRMs）会像人一样'解释过程'：先分析，再推理，然后再给结论，使搜索排序不仅更准确，也更可解释。",
    "SAM 让强化学习从'只看结果'变为'理解过程'。",
    "我们的工作首次在小红书搜索中验证了一条可规模化落地的新路径：用 RL 驱动生成式相关性判断，通过规则引导推理链，并利用 SAM 精准分配奖励信号。"
  ],
